story of Japanese Literature (page does not exist)\">Japanese Literature</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=The_Cambridge_History_of_Latin_American_Literature&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"The Cambridge History of Latin American Literature (page does not exist)\">Latin American Literature</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=The_Cambridge_History_of_Literary_Criticism&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"The Cambridge History of Literary Criticism (page does not exist)\">Literary Criticism</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=The_Cambridge_History_of_Russian_Literature&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"The Cambridge History of Russian Literature (page does not exist)\">Russian Literature</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=The_Cambridge_History_of_South_African_Literature&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"The Cambridge History of South African Literature (page does not exist)\">South African Literature</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=The_Cambridge_History_of_Spanish_Literature&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"The Cambridge History of Spanish Literature (page does not exist)\">Spanish Literature</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">Religion</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-even hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=The_Cambridge_History_of_the_Bible&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"The Cambridge History of the Bible (page does not exist)\">Bible</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=The_Cambridge_History_of_Christianity&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"The Cambridge History of Christianity (page does not exist)\">Christianity</a></li>\n<li>Islam\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/The_Cambridge_Histo